{"tid":1955150,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"究竟你地知唔知點解大圍捕同鳩拉？由今日件事就知根本係為咗你部電話","createTime":"2020-04-02T10:00:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-02T12:38:05.000Z","uid":188828,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"8e4490449a96621deaf901ca1c571fc3b59e6a3b","tid":1955150,"uid":188828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T10:00:30.000Z","msg":"有冇人發現<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">近幾個月啲狗愈來愈中意鳩拉人</span></span><br />\n根本你認為<span style=\"color: red;\">唔應該有罪名告唔入佢都照拉</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">知唔知點解？</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">因為想要你地部手機</span><br />\n<br />\n即使告唔入你最後踢保都唔會可以咁快拎得返部手機<br />\n有咗你地部手機<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">你身邊既人會被起底</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">你同你家人朋友會被自殺被消失<br />\n你隊友會被上門拘捕</span><br />\n<br />\n所以唔好再講坐48唔緊要<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">除非你帶部舊到冇人有又冇重要野既手機出街<br />\n然後張平時用既收好<br />\n一個你知道同平全既地方</span><br />\n<br />\n我知聽落好撚麻煩<br />\n但你聽我講<br />\n為咗自己同身邊人既安全<br />\n真係要咁做<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">特別係有小隊或者做實事既手足</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">每次出黎帶部舊電話</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">每次出黎帶部舊電話</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">每次出黎帶部舊電話</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n食花生友 做哨 做街坊都要"},{"pid":"9e34b667a096b34ef32866aaddaf754dc8890e8c","tid":1955150,"uid":188828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T10:00:54.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"f0f7e9e014b2dbbda3c61ec82796c7e087f94098","tid":1955150,"uid":188828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T10:01:09.000Z","msg":"自推2"},{"pid":"34ba3a5376c7a1de4ee36289ead18afcc2b93bce","tid":1955150,"uid":188828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi